@startuml Candidate_Applications

title Candidate - Job Applications (Module D)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng Viên"

rectangle "APPLICATIONS" {
    usecase "Submit\nApplication" as D1
    usecase "List My\nApplications" as D2
    usecase "View Application\nDetails" as D4
    usecase "View Status\nHistory" as D8
    usecase "Cancel\nApplication" as D6
}

Candidate --> D1: 1. Submit application
Candidate --> D2: 2. View my applications
D2 --> D4: 3. View details
D4 --> D8: 4. Check status history
D4 --> D6: 5. Cancel application

note right of D1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Implemented ✅
end note

@enduml
